"# Product Context — PawPilot

## Why this exists
Pet owners struggle to keep track of their pets' health records, appointments, and medications across multiple vet visits and providers.

## How it should work
A unified platform that centralizes pet health management with appointment scheduling, digital health records, medication reminders, and direct vet communication.

## Target users
- Pet owners
- Veterinarians
- Pet care providers

## User stories
- As a pet owner, I want to store my pet's health records in one place.
- As a veterinarian, I want to access a pet's medical history before an appointment.

## MVP scope
- Pet profile creation with health records
- Appointment scheduling with calendar view
- Medication tracking with reminders
- Vet communication via in-app messaging

## Quality rules
- Pet health data must be stored securely
- Appointment scheduling must prevent double-booking
"
`;

