"# Product Context — Travel Planner

## Why this exists
Planning a trip involves juggling multiple tabs, spreadsheets, and apps for flights, hotels, activities, and budgets, leading to a fragmented experience.

## How it should work
A unified trip planning platform with AI-powered destination discovery, collaborative itinerary building, budget tracking, and sharing features.

## Target users
- Travel enthusiasts
- Trip planners
- Group travelers

## User stories
- As a traveler, I want AI suggestions for destinations based on my preferences.
- As a group traveler, I want to collaborate on the itinerary with my companions.

## MVP scope
- Destination discovery with AI suggestions
- Itinerary builder with drag-and-drop
- Budget tracker per trip
- Trip sharing with companions

## Quality rules
- Itinerary must support date ranges
- Budget must calculate totals correctly
"
